OL,2,MThe Marvellous Mouse-powered Music box
OL,4,CMiranda
OL,5,CSat 13:20-13:40
OL,6,CStage C
OL,8,GIt started when I stupidly promising
OL,9,Gmy 8 year old that if the mouse
OL,10,Gbrought in by my cat made through the
OL,11,Gnight, we could keep it. It ended with
OL,12,Ga beautiful rendition of Toccata in D
OL,13,Gplayed solely by the rising star Mr
OL,14,GCheesey and the contraption I attached
OL,15,Gto his wheel. In this talk, I’ll cover
OL,16,Gthe ideas behind the plans, the
OL,17,Gdesigning and development of the music
OL,18,Gbox wheel, the challenges of actually
OL,19,Gmaking it into a real machine (when
OL,20,Gsome of there parts didn’t even exist)
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
